title: Manatee

creator: Shawn Kuenzler
descriptionHtml:
Connect with your kid. See progress. Grow together.
Join our 6-week evidence-based course to help families conquer anxiety.
Called “groundbreaking” and “first of its kind” by parents and at least two teenagers who didn’t roll their eyes ;)

Be your kids’ ally in their mental health journey
Use goals and rewards to show progress
Practice coping skills like journaling
Learn via courses for parents and kids
Manatee is a family-first mental health app, designed for kids and families living in the modern world. We are engaging, comprehensive, evidence-based and most importantly, designed to get results.
The app and our programs drive emotional well-being by supercharging skills to build healthy family relationships and resilience.

Features of the app include:
* Goals - choose from our library of evidence-based goals or set your own to work on. If working through the course, Manatee will assign parents and kids their weekly goals, no-brainer.
* Rewards - talk with your kid to come up with the rewards that will be most exciting and motivating for them and celebrate their goal successes.
* Chatbot - interacts with your kid to provide exercises based on cognitive behavioral therapy and mindfulness
* Journaling - kids use helpful prompts to write and share their feelings daily
* Learnings - 6 weeks of self-guided lessons to help your family conquer anxiety including weekly content, activities, and more!
* Check-ins - for children over 12, regular short surveys assess how they are doing and progressing
* Include co-parents - it takes a village to raise a kid so you can add as many “co-parents” as you wish to the same kid account. This could be a co-parent, nanny, grandparent...you get the idea.

***Celebrate progress and build confidence***

All kids who complete the learning course will get their own pet manatee with a state-of-the-art indoor aquarium. Kidding...bonus points for reading this far though!

How does it work?
Parents, install the app on your device first and sign up for our first anxiety course (more courses to come!)

title: Manatee: Mental health for families

creator: Manatee, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Manatee is here to help your family grow closer together and thrive! We empower parents and kids with resources to learn more about each other, build healthy habits, tools to cope with big feelings, and connect more deeply.

Every family can benefit from Manatee, but especially if:
- The harmony in your family feels off…
- Day-to-day activities are a struggle
- You’re worried about your kid, but not sure what is ‘normal’
- You feel like you’re just surviving… not thriving!
- You could use some support, but don’t know where to start
- You just want to be the best parent you can be!

Are you looking for a little more?
You’d like to explore family or child therapy? Parent coaching? No need to look any further!
You can match with a licensed therapist as soon as TODAY.
Families who need additional support have NO WAITLIST access to a team of family experts, like licensed therapists and parent coaches and will continue to use our app to supercharge your family’s treatment, too.

MANATEE’S FEATURES
- Goals: Build healthy habits as a family. Encourage kids to build their self-esteem, give them tools to work on big feelings, and more.
- Rewards: Fun family rewards that will help you celebrate success.
- Chatbot: Built to interact with your kid and provide mindfulness exercises.
- Journal: A safe space for kids to untangle their thoughts.
- Courses: Lessons developed by experts and loved by parents.
- Family connection: Come together as a family and learn something new about each other!
Families in our clinical care also have access to the following features:
- Instant messaging with their team of care coordinators, therapists or coaches.
- A treatment plan with goals tailored for their family’s needs.
- Regular check-ins and assessments to track progress.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Your family can use Manatee independently. It’s pretty simple: download the app and add your kid(s) and any co-parents or caregivers to your account. Then set up your goals, rewards, and maybe pick a self-guided course, and you’re good to go!
But… If you feel like your family needs more support, then we’ve got your back there, too. The Manatee app works best as a companion to our Family Care model! Here’s how that works:
1. Book your consult
Have a free 20-minute call with a family expert so we can get to know your family. If it’s a good fit, we’ll schedule your intake session.
2. Assessment and intake
After you complete your assessment, you’ll review your results with your therapist, discuss your family’s unique needs and create your 6-week care plan together.
3. Start your 6-week care plan
It’s time to get your family’s groove back! Our care plan includes weekly therapy/coaching sessions and our family app that helps put your hard earned knowledge into practice.

0.194.0

creator: Manatee, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Manatee is here to help your family grow closer together and thrive! We empower parents and kids with resources to learn more about each other, build healthy habits, tools to cope with big feelings, and connect more deeply.

Every family can benefit from Manatee, but especially if:
- The harmony in your family feels off…
- Day-to-day activities are a struggle
- You’re worried about your kid, but not sure what is ‘normal’
- You feel like you’re just surviving… not thriving!
- You could use some support, but don’t know where to start
- You just want to be the best parent you can be!

Are you looking for a little more?
You’d like to explore family or child therapy? Parent coaching? No need to look any further!
You can match with a licensed therapist as soon as TODAY.
Families who need additional support have NO WAITLIST access to a team of family experts, like licensed therapists and parent coaches and will continue to use our app to supercharge your family’s treatment, too.

MANATEE’S FEATURES
- Goals: Build healthy habits as a family. Encourage kids to build their self-esteem, give them tools to work on big feelings, and more.
- Rewards: Fun family rewards that will help you celebrate success.
- Chatbot: Built to interact with your kid and provide mindfulness exercises.
- Journal: A safe space for kids to untangle their thoughts.
- Courses: Lessons developed by experts and loved by parents.
- Family connection: Come together as a family and learn something new about each other!
Families in our clinical care also have access to the following features:
- Instant messaging with their team of care coordinators, therapists or coaches.
- A treatment plan with goals tailored for their family’s needs.
- Regular check-ins and assessments to track progress.

HOW DOES IT WORK?
Your family can use Manatee independently. It’s pretty simple: download the app and add your kid(s) and any co-parents or caregivers to your account. Then set up your goals, rewards, and maybe pick a self-guided course, and you’re good to go!
But… If you feel like your family needs more support, then we’ve got your back there, too. The Manatee app works best as a companion to our Family Care model! Here’s how that works:
1. Book your consult
Have a free 20-minute call with a family expert so we can get to know your family. If it’s a good fit, we’ll schedule your intake session.
2. Assessment and intake
After you complete your assessment, you’ll review your results with your therapist, discuss your family’s unique needs and create your 6-week care plan together.
3. Start your 6-week care plan
It’s time to get your family’s groove back! Our care plan includes weekly therapy/coaching sessions and our family app that helps put your hard earned knowledge into practice.
